trans-unit.source: Specifies the bullet styles you can apply to list items in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Angir de punktstilene listeelementer i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The BulletStyle enumeration represents the bullet styles that you can apply to the list items in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList> control.
trans-unit.target: Opplistingen BulletStyle representerer punktstiler som du kan bruke på listeelementer i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList.BulletStyle%2A> property uses these enumeration values to set the bullet styles in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList> control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList.BulletStyle%2A>disse nummereringsverdier bruker til å angi punktstiler i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList.BulletStyle%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, if you set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList.BulletStyle%2A> property to `Disc`, each list item in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList> control will render a filled circle preceding the content of the list item as follows: - List Item 1 - List Item 2 - List Item 3 Specifying the `CustomImage` bullet style allows you to supply your own image for the bullet.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis du angir den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList.BulletStyle%2A>egenskapen `Disc`, hvert listeelement i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList>kontrollen skal gjengi en sirkel foregående innholdet i listeelementet som følger: - listen elementet 1 - listeelementet 2 - listen elementet 3 angivelse av `CustomImage` Punktstil lar deg angi ditt eget bilde for punktet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList.BulletStyle%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you specify the `CustomImage` bullet style, you must also set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList.BulletImageUrl%2A> property to the URL of the custom image to use.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du angir den `CustomImage` Punktstil, må du også angi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList.BulletImageUrl%2A>URL-adresse for den egendefinerte avbildningen å bruke egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList.BulletImageUrl%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you specify `NotSet`, the browser in which the control is rendered will determine the bullet style to display with the list items in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList> control.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du angir `NotSet`, nettleseren kontrollen gjengis bestemmer Punktstil skal vises med listeelementer i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.BulletedList>
